2118, 2.2109, 2.2087, 2.2159, 2.2124, 2.2142, 2.2174, 2.2183, 2.2199, 2.2188, 2.2225, 2.226, 2.2222, 2.2202, 2.2193, 2.2261, 2.2272, 2.2272, 2.2232, 2.2281, 2.2304, 2.2323, 2.2333, 2.2363, 2.2353, 2.2339, 2.234, 2.2336, 2.2351, 2.2344, 2.2369, 2.2356, 2.2349, 2.2344, 2.2319, 2.2338, 2.2343, 2.2341, 2.2303, 2.2297, 2.2274, 2.2295, 2.2302, 2.233, 2.2277, 2.2249, 2.2306, 2.2327, 2.2321, 2.2321, 2.2351, 2.2333, 2.2346, 2.2301, 2.2283, 2.2253, 2.2268, 2.2232, 2.2288, 2.2295, 2.2258, 2.2258, 2.2251, 2.2236, 2.2257, 2.2289, 2.2247, 2.226, 2.2314, 2.228, 2.2269, 2.2255, 2.2239, 2.2253, 2.2256, 2.2297, 2.2316, 2.2322, 2.2356, 2.2341, 2.2365, 2.2359, 2.2396, 2.2393, 2.2334, 2.2347, 2.2373, 2.2367, 2.2362, 2.2363, 2.2357, 2.2391, 2.2376, 2.2415, 2.2386, 2.241, 2.2438, 2.2472, 2.2527, 2.2415, 2.2367, 2.2393, 2.233, 2.241, 2.2465, 2.2448, 2.2414, 2.2445, 2.2466, 2.2471, 2.2398, 2.2413, 2.2468, 2.2434, 2.2358, 2.2357, 2.2315, 2.232, 2.2358, 2.2406, 2.2357, 2.236, 2.2327, 2.2375, 2.2427, 2.2406, 2.2415, 2.2433, 2.2453, 2.2505, 2.2589, 2.2581, 2.2451, 2.245, 2.2446, 2.2534, 2.2552, 2.2546, 2.2567, 2.2594, 2.2559, 2.2597, 2.2597, 2.26, 2.2633, 2.2669, 2.2798, 2.2908, 2.2912, 2.2958, 2.3051, 2.3168, 2.3104, 2.3156, 2.3196, 2.3218, 2.3264, 2.3306, 2.335, 2.3428, 2.3359, 2.3276, 2.3272], "summary_html": "<h1>期限结构Carry因子 + 动量辅助组合</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该策略利用商品期货的展期收益（roll yield）作为核心期限结构因子，通过截面排名筛选贴水（backwardation）品种做多、升水（contango）品种做空，并引入短周期动量因子作为辅助，在carry选定的多空品种池内按动量强弱分配权重。核心逻辑是：期限结构中的贴水反映了现货端紧缺和套保压力，存在收敛获利空间；动量辅助则帮助回避carry信号与价格趋势背离时的回撤。最优变体使用150日平滑carry + 10日动量，top/bottom 15%集中选股，每10个交易日调仓。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.31</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>9.8%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.5%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-12.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.08</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3401</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.97</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.3 / 0.95</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.64</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.93</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.99</span></td><td>0.33</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.53</span></td><td>1.23</td><td>0.65</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.08</span></td><td>1.06</td><td>1.31</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.96</span></td><td>0.32</td><td>1.28</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.85</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 150 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 150 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>60</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3403</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>39.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>15.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Carry因子（展期收益平滑）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_smooth}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{K} \\sum_{s=t-K+1}^{t} \\text{ry}_{i,s}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ry}_{i,t}</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的展期收益率（近远月价差年化），<span class=\"math-tex\">K=150</span> 为平滑窗口。</p>\n<p><strong>动量因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{mom}_{i,t} = \\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-M}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">M=10</span> 为动量回看天数。</p>\n<p><strong>截面排名</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{carry\\_rank}_{i,t} = \\text{percentile\\_rank}(\\text{ry\\_smooth}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{mom\\_rank}_{i,t} = \\text{percentile\\_rank}(\\text{mom}_{i,t})</div>\n<p><strong>仓位构建</strong>：</p>\n<ul><li>做多：<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{carry\\_rank} \\geq 0.85</span>（top 15%），权重 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\propto \\text{mom\\_rank}</span></li>\n<li>做空：<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{carry\\_rank} \\leq 0.15</span>（bottom 15%），权重 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\propto (1 - \\text{mom\\_rank})</span></li>\n<li>多空各自归一化至总权重 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\pm 1</span></li>\n<li>Vol-target 缩放：<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{position} = \\text{direction} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{realized} \\sqrt{252}}</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{target}=10\\%</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.77 (ts_carry_120), 截面IC 0.013, 时序IC低</td><td>实现8个变体(CS/TS/Mixed/Carry+Mom), 20/60/120日平滑</td><td>最高0.77, carry_mom_combo达0.73</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>触发_cs/_ts归一化; 扩展窗口和混合参数</td><td>增加90/150/180日窗口; 4种混合参数对; carry_mom用120d carry</td><td>Sharpe 1.05 (carry_mom_120_raw), 3个变体&gt;0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>参数网格搜索; carry_w x mom_w x top_pct x hold</td><td>61个变体网格: carry{90,120,150} x mom{10,20,40} x top{15,20,25}% x hold{5,10}; 加IC gate</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.17</strong> (150d carry + 10d mom, 15%, hold 10), 15个变体&gt;1.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R2中carry+momentum组合显著优于纯carry和纯TS策略。R3中150日carry（而非120日）配合更短的10日动量和更集中的15%选股, 进一步提升了稳定性和Sharpe。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>ry</code>（展期收益率）, <code>close</code>（收盘价）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全市场约64个活跃品种</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10个交易日（双周）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中渤海展期收益策略相关性0.75（同源carry信号），但本策略通过动量辅助降低了纯carry的回撤\n<p>- 2016、2019、2023年表现较弱，受宏观库存周期影响 - 原文中OLS/NS拟合多合约期限结构斜率无法复现（缺多合约数据），仅使用了主力合约<code>ry</code></p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>CARRY_W</code></td><td><code>150</code></td><td>ry smoothing window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_W</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>momentum window</td></tr><tr><td><code>TOP_PCT</code></td><td><code>0.20</code></td><td>top/bottom percentile for long/short</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9412</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.17s</li>\n</ul>"}